### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

###

### 1. Collect User Tweets
POST http://localhost:3001/api/tweets/collect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID",
  "max_tweets": 100
}

###

### 2. Get Stored Tweets
GET http://localhost:3001/api/tweets/YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID?limit=10&offset=0

###

### 3. Generate Tweet Drafts (Example 1)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/drafts/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID",
  "idea": "Shipping builds momentum. Momentum builds confidence. Confidence builds companies.",
  "num_variations": 3,
  "top_k": 5
}

###

### 4. Generate Tweet Drafts (Example 2)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/drafts/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID",
  "idea": "Building features is useless if nobody sees them. Shipping matters more.",
  "num_variations": 3
}

###

### 5. Regenerate with Different Variations
POST http://localhost:3001/api/drafts/regenerate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID",
  "idea": "Shipping builds momentum",
  "previous_drafts": [
    "First draft that wasn't good enough",
    "Second draft that was too generic"
  ]
}

###

### 6. Get User's Draft History
GET http://localhost:3001/api/drafts/YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID?limit=10

###

### 7. Get User's Style Profile
GET http://localhost:3001/api/drafts/YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID/profile

###

### 8. Delete User Tweets and Embeddings
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/tweets/YOUR_TWITTER_USER_ID

###
